{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "tms-parking-validation-v4",
    "name": "TMS Parking Validation",
    "description": "## TMS Parking Validation API — v4\n\n### Login Flow\n\n**Two modes, one endpoint `POST /api/auth/login`:**\n\n- **MODE 1 — OAuth Bearer**: set `oauthBearerToken` variable → script injects it as `Authorization: Bearer`.\n- **MODE 2 — Username/Password**: leave `oauthBearerToken` empty, set `username` + `password`.\n\n**Both modes return `LoginResponse`:**\n```json\n{\n  \"tmsToken\":       \"<HS256 JWT — use as Bearer on all calls>\",\n  \"role\":           \"TENANT_ADMIN\",\n  \"tenantId\":       \"uuid\",\n  \"clientId\":       \"uuid\",\n  \"subTenantId\":    null,\n  \"assignedTenants\": [],\n  \"email\":          \"user@example.com\",\n  \"name\":           \"Jane Doe\",\n  \"message\":        null\n}\n```\n\n### Roles (5 levels)\n`ADMIN` > `CLIENT_ADMIN` > `TENANT_ADMIN` > `SUB_TENANT_ADMIN` > `USER`\n\n### Quick Start\n1. Set `password` (and `username` if different).\n2. Run **Login** — `accessToken`, `role`, `tenantId`, `clientId`, `subTenantId` are auto-saved.\n3. All protected requests inherit `Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}` from the collection auth.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",           "value": "http://localhost:8080",            "type": "string" },
    { "key": "oauthBaseUrl",      "value": "http://localhost:9090",            "type": "string", "description": "OAuth server (server-side only)" },
    { "key": "username",          "value": "venu.kannuri@optimus-ai.com",      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "password",          "value": "",                                 "type": "string", "description": "Set before running Login" },
    { "key": "oauthBearerToken",  "value": "",                                 "type": "string", "description": "Set to OAuth RS256 token for MODE 1. Leave empty for MODE 2." },
    { "key": "accessToken",       "value": "",                                 "type": "string", "description": "TMS HS256 JWT — set by Login, used as Bearer" },
    { "key": "userId",            "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "role",              "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "tenantId",          "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "clientId",          "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "subTenantId",       "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "assignedTenants",   "value": "[]",                               "type": "string", "description": "JSON array of UUID strings — populated for CLIENT_ADMIN" },
    { "key": "zoneId",            "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "linkId",            "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "linkToken",         "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "validationId",      "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "reportJobId",       "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "quotaConfigId",     "value": "",                                 "type": "string" },
    { "key": "targetUserId",      "value": "",                                 "type": "string", "description": "UUID of the user to modify (not yourself)" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "description": "Authentication — TMS HS256 token flow.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (OAuth → TMS token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const oauthToken = pm.collectionVariables.get('oauthBearerToken');",
                  "if (oauthToken) {",
                  "    pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'Authorization', value: 'Bearer ' + oauthToken });",
                  "    pm.request.body.raw = '';",
                  "    console.log('MODE 1: OAuth Bearer token');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    pm.request.headers.remove('Authorization');",
                  "    console.log('MODE 2: username/password');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Has tmsToken', () => pm.expect(res.tmsToken).to.be.a('string').and.have.length.above(10));",
                  "pm.test('Has role',     () => pm.expect(res.role).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.tmsToken);",
                  "if (res.role)        pm.collectionVariables.set('role',        res.role);",
                  "if (res.tenantId)    pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantId',    res.tenantId);",
                  "if (res.clientId)    pm.collectionVariables.set('clientId',    res.clientId);",
                  "if (res.subTenantId) pm.collectionVariables.set('subTenantId', res.subTenantId);",
                  "if (res.assignedTenants) pm.collectionVariables.set('assignedTenants', JSON.stringify(res.assignedTenants));",
                  "try {",
                  "    const parts = res.tmsToken.split('.');",
                  "    if (parts.length === 3) {",
                  "        const b64 = parts[1].replace(/-/g,'+').replace(/_/g,'/');",
                  "        const p = JSON.parse(atob(b64 + '='.repeat((4 - b64.length%4)%4)));",
                  "        if (p.sub) pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', p.sub);",
                  "        pm.test('JWT not expired', () => pm.expect(p.exp*1000).to.be.above(Date.now()));",
                  "        console.log('userId:', p.sub, '| role:', res.role, '| tenantId:', res.tenantId || '(none)');",
                  "        if (res.assignedTenants && res.assignedTenants.length) {",
                  "            console.log('CLIENT_ADMIN assignedTenants:', res.assignedTenants);",
                  "        }",
                  "    }",
                  "} catch (e) { console.error('Cannot decode JWT:', e.message); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{username}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "## Login — Two Modes\n\n### MODE 1 — OAuth Bearer token\nSet `oauthBearerToken` collection variable to your OAuth RS256 token.\n\n### MODE 2 — Username + Password\nLeave `oauthBearerToken` empty. Set `username` + `password`.\n\n### Response `LoginResponse`:\n```json\n{\n  \"tmsToken\":       \"<HS256 JWT>\",\n  \"role\":           \"TENANT_ADMIN\",\n  \"tenantId\":       \"uuid-or-null\",\n  \"clientId\":       \"uuid-or-null\",\n  \"subTenantId\":    null,\n  \"assignedTenants\": [\"uuid1\",\"uuid2\"],\n  \"email\":          \"user@example.com\",\n  \"name\":           \"Jane Doe\",\n  \"message\":        null\n}\n```\n\n`assignedTenants` is populated only for `CLIENT_ADMIN`.\nTest script saves `accessToken = tmsToken`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Token Exchange (OAuth RS256 → TMS HS256)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Has tmsToken', () => pm.expect(res.tmsToken).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', res.tmsToken);",
                  "if (res.role)        pm.collectionVariables.set('role',        res.role);",
                  "if (res.tenantId)    pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantId',    res.tenantId);",
                  "if (res.clientId)    pm.collectionVariables.set('clientId',    res.clientId);",
                  "if (res.subTenantId) pm.collectionVariables.set('subTenantId', res.subTenantId);",
                  "if (res.assignedTenants) pm.collectionVariables.set('assignedTenants', JSON.stringify(res.assignedTenants));",
                  "try {",
                  "    const parts = res.tmsToken.split('.');",
                  "    const b64 = parts[1].replace(/-/g,'+').replace(/_/g,'/');",
                  "    const p = JSON.parse(atob(b64 + '='.repeat((4-b64.length%4)%4)));",
                  "    if (p.sub) pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', p.sub);",
                  "    console.log('Exchanged | userId:', p.sub, '| role:', res.role);",
                  "} catch (e) { console.error('Cannot decode:', e.message); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"oauthToken\": \"PASTE_YOUR_OAUTH_RS256_TOKEN_HERE\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/token-exchange",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "token-exchange"]
            },
            "description": "Exchange an OAuth RS256 token for a TMS HS256 internal JWT.\n\nReturns the same `LoginResponse` shape as Login."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me (Current User)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Has userId', () => pm.expect(res.userId).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('Has email',  () => pm.expect(res.email).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('Has roles',  () => pm.expect(res.roles).to.be.an('array').with.length.above(0));",
                  "if (res.tenantId)        pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantId',        res.tenantId);",
                  "if (res.clientId)        pm.collectionVariables.set('clientId',        res.clientId);",
                  "if (res.subTenantId)     pm.collectionVariables.set('subTenantId',     res.subTenantId);",
                  "if (res.assignedTenants) pm.collectionVariables.set('assignedTenants', JSON.stringify(res.assignedTenants));",
                  "console.log('Me:', res.email, '| userId:', res.userId, '| roles:', res.roles);",
                  "if (res.assignedTenants && res.assignedTenants.length) {",
                  "    console.log('CLIENT_ADMIN tenants:', res.assignedTenants);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Returns current user profile decoded from JWT — no DB round-trip.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\":          \"auth0|abc123\",\n  \"email\":           \"user@example.com\",\n  \"name\":            null,\n  \"tenantId\":        \"uuid\",\n  \"clientId\":        \"uuid\",\n  \"subTenantId\":     null,\n  \"roles\":           [\"TENANT_ADMIN\"],\n  \"assignedTenants\": []\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 204', () => pm.response.to.have.status(204));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', '');",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('role', '');",
                  "console.log('Logged out — accessToken cleared.');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Returns `204 No Content`. Clears `accessToken` from collection variables."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "👥 Users",
      "description": "**Role restriction:** `CLIENT_ADMIN` can only assign `TENANT_ADMIN`, `SUB_TENANT_ADMIN`, `USER`. Assigning `ADMIN` or `CLIENT_ADMIN` returns `403`.\n\nAfter any role/tenant change the user must **re-login** for the JWT to reflect the change.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users?page=0&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{targetUserId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{targetUserId}}"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User's Assigned Tenants",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{targetUserId}}/assigned-tenants",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{targetUserId}}", "assigned-tenants"]
            },
            "description": "Returns the list of tenant UUIDs assigned to a `CLIENT_ADMIN` user. Returns `[]` for non-CLIENT_ADMIN."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Assign Role",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Has message', () => pm.expect(res.message).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "console.log('Role assigned:', res.message);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"role\": \"TENANT_ADMIN\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{targetUserId}}/role",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{targetUserId}}", "role"]
            },
            "description": "**Valid roles:** `ADMIN`, `CLIENT_ADMIN`, `TENANT_ADMIN`, `SUB_TENANT_ADMIN`, `USER`\n\n**Restriction:** `CLIENT_ADMIN` callers cannot assign `ADMIN` or `CLIENT_ADMIN` → `403`.\n\nUser must re-login after role change."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Assign Tenant",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tenantId\":    \"{{tenantId}}\",\n  \"clientId\":    \"{{clientId}}\",\n  \"subTenantId\": null\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{targetUserId}}/tenant",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{targetUserId}}", "tenant"]
            },
            "description": "`subTenantId` is optional — set `null` for TENANT_ADMIN. User must re-login after change."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Deactivate User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('isActive is false', () => pm.expect(res.active).to.equal(false));",
                  "console.log('Deactivated user:', res.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{targetUserId}}/deactivate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users", "{{targetUserId}}", "deactivate"]
            },
            "description": "Sets `isActive = false`. Deactivated users cannot log in — LoginService returns `403` on next login attempt."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🏢 Clients",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Clients",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clients?page=0&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "clients"],
              "query": [{ "key": "page", "value": "0" }, { "key": "size", "value": "20" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Client",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clients/{{clientId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","clients","{{clientId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Client",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));","const res = pm.response.json();","if (res.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('clientId', res.id);","console.log('Created client:', res.id);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Acme Parking Co.\",\n  \"plan\": \"STANDARD\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clients", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","clients"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Client",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Acme Parking Co. (Updated)\",\n  \"plan\": \"ENTERPRISE\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clients/{{clientId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","clients","{{clientId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Client",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/clients/{{clientId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","clients","{{clientId}}"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🏗️ Tenants",
      "description": "**Scoping:** `ADMIN` sees all. `CLIENT_ADMIN` sees only `assignedTenants` (or clientId fallback). Creating a tenant auto-assigns the `CLIENT_ADMIN` caller.\n\nAfter assign/unassign-admin the target user must re-login.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Tenants",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants?page=0&size=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "tenants"],
              "query": [{ "key": "page", "value": "0" }, { "key": "size", "value": "20" }]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Tenant",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","tenants","{{tenantId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Tenant",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));","const res = pm.response.json();","if (res.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantId', res.id);","console.log('Created tenant:', res.id, res.name);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"clientId\": \"{{clientId}}\",\n  \"name\": \"Downtown Parkade\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","tenants"] },
            "description": "`clientId` optional for `CLIENT_ADMIN` (defaults to their own). New tenant is auto-added to `CLIENT_ADMIN`'s `assignedTenants`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Tenant",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Downtown Parkade (Updated)\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","tenants","{{tenantId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Tenant",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","tenants","{{tenantId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Assign CLIENT_ADMIN to Tenant  🔒 ADMIN only",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));","const res = pm.response.json();","pm.test('Has message', () => pm.expect(res.message).to.be.a('string'));","console.log(res.message);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{targetUserId}}\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/assign-admin",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "tenants", "{{tenantId}}", "assign-admin"]
            },
            "description": "**ADMIN only.** Grants a `CLIENT_ADMIN` user access to this tenant via `client_admin_tenants` table.\n\nIdempotent. User must re-login for change to take effect.\n\n**Response:** `{ \"message\": \"Admin assigned. User must re-login for changes to take effect.\" }`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Unassign CLIENT_ADMIN from Tenant  🔒 ADMIN only",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));","console.log(pm.response.json().message);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{targetUserId}}\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/unassign-admin",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "tenants", "{{tenantId}}", "unassign-admin"]
            },
            "description": "**ADMIN only.** Removes CLIENT_ADMIN access. User must re-login."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Branding (Public — no auth)",
